column2: SELECT p.objId, p.ra, p.dec, p.petror9#_r, p.expAB_r, p.dered_u as u, p.dered_g as g, p.dered_r as r, p.dered_i as i, s.z, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, i.v_disp FROM galaxy AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN galSpecInfo as i ON i.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE p.ra between # and # and s.z > #
